  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Deadheat Road is a classic racing game in which the player compete in a racing againts a computer player car. The races usually starts in the night and ends with the daylight. The game features different cars for the player to choose and different circuits (west and east ones). The cars can also be customized.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Road race that starts on the highway, and makes its way into a metropolis!\nPlenty of racing to fully enjoy in a powerful presence of realistic 3D perspective using polygon graphics.",
